{"title":"洗浴","icon":"bath","grey":true,"shareable":true,"id":"guide/bath/index","author":"Mr.Hope","cite":[],"content":[{"tag":"text","type":"info","header":"简介","text":["由于宿舍没有独立卫浴，学校两校区均设有公共浴池。学生浴池采用单间设计，保证了洗浴的舒适性、便利性、私密性和安全性。","净月校区浴池配备了免费健身房，两校区浴池均设有休息厅以及便民商家服务。"]},{"tag":"list","items":[{"text":"如何洗浴","icon":"bath","path":"guide/bath/usage"}]},{"tag":"list","header":"浴池介绍","items":[{"text":"本部","path":"guide/bath/benbu"},{"text":"净月","path":"guide/bath/jingyue"}]},{"tag":"list","header":"浴池账户","items":[{"text":"提供商与计费","icon":"account","path":"guide/bath/account"},{"text":"浴池充值","icon":"charge","path":"guide/bath/charge"},{"text":"浴池金额查看","icon":"money","path":"guide/bath/money"},{"text":"浴池提现","icon":"change","path":"guide/bath/cash"}]}],"time":"2025 年 7 月 11 日 07:56:14"}